{
  "name": "Reality Bender",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Kurama.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Kurama Clan, Level 16+</p><p>You have deepened your control of the perceived reality. <br />You gain the following benefits:</p><p><br />• Your Genjutsu Resistance bonus is increased by +2. </p><p><br />• The cost reduction from Genjutsu Specialty is increased to: <br />(D-Rank: 2, C-Rank: 3, B-Rank: 4, A-Rank: 5, S-Rank: 6.)</p><p> </p><p>• You treat successes as Critical successes when you pass a Genjutsu save. </p><p><br />• If you pass a Genjutsu save, you may as a reaction attempt to cast the jutsu back on the caster. <br />Make a Wisdom (Illusions) check vs the targets Genjutsu save DC. <br />On a success, you cast the jutsu right back at them. <br />Attempting this reaction requires you to have all the necessary keywords and components associated with the jutsu</p>",
